# Example x64 verification run (see the "Running for `x64`" section of the
# README).
#
# Verifies the possible expansions for the base case of an x64 `iadd` of 32- or
# 64-bit values. `--name` selects the x64 ISLE compilation unit and `--rule`
# scopes to the single `lower` rule (and its downstream chained rules).
--name x64
--rule iadd_base_case_32_or_64_lea
